"POSIX.1-2001, POSIX.1-2008, 4.4BSD, SVr4 (these calls first appeared in "
"4.2BSD)."
msgstr ""
"POSIX.1-2001, POSIX.1-2008, 4.4BSD, SVr4 (diese Systemaufrufe traten zuerst "
"in BSD 4.2 auf)."

